halo-vllm-docker
================

This project is a scaffold derived from the structure of:

    spark-vllm-docker
    Copyright (c) 2026 Eugene Rakhmatulin
    https://github.com/eugr/spark-vllm-docker
    Licensed under the MIT License.

The original targets NVIDIA DGX Spark (GB10 / CUDA / ARM64). This repository
re-targets the same idea at AMD Strix Halo (Radeon 8060S / gfx1151 / ROCm).

IMPORTANT: This is currently a SCAFFOLD ONLY. The directory layout and file
skeletons mirror the original project, but the ROCm/Halo implementation has
NOT yet been written or validated on hardware. Files marked "SCAFFOLD" /
"TODO" contain placeholders, not working code. Do not assume any Dockerfile,
script, or recipe here builds or runs until it has been filled in and tested
on a real Strix Halo machine.
